metadata.name: Richie and Cherry
metadata.description:
Once in the autumn forest...

A cute little fox girl named Cherry was walking through the woods. Suddenly she saw Richie. It was a cute corgi. Thanks to the red color and fluffy tail, Richie was very similar to a small fox cub. Cherry immediately fell in love with Ricci. She takes care of him like an older sister and doesn't let anyone get too close to Richie.
